headline: Palantir Is Now a $400 Billion-Plus Company
summary: Palantir Technologies, the data software specialist, is now worth more than Salesforce and Adobe combined. By the numbers:    Palantir ended Tuesday with a market capitalization of about $411 billion, according to Dow Jones Market Data—the first time it has closed above the $400 billion threshold.
